				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${D}_{4h}^{9}$$\end{document}29,44 with lattice parameters a = 0.3043 nm and c = 0.5337 nm. The measurement of the X-ray diffraction line width showed that the minimum crystallites size of Ag-Pd and PdO are 39 and 28 nm, respectively32.
